v18

## Changes

* Adds Nix 2.11.0

* Changes default Nix version from 2.10.3 to 2.11.0

* Improves error message when SSH key is invalid or inaccessible


## Known issues

* `macos-latest` not currently not supported, use `macos-10.15` instead.
  See https://github.com/nixbuild/nix-quick-install-action/issues/7
